Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.10,0:00:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Dr. David Hawkins. I'm a physician. I've been a psychiatrist for 35 years, worked in the field
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.76,0:00:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,of psychoanalysis, worked in the field of nutrition, and especially nutrition and its relationship to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.30,0:00:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,brain chemistry. For the last 10 years, I've been doing research into the nature of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,itself, and especially its relationship to that which the world calls spiritual. In today's talk,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.00,0:00:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,we're going to be looking at the subject of health, one which everyone is interested in,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.44,0:00:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the subject of health which occupies the minds of a large part of our population. And of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.10,0:00:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,as a physician, and as a psychiatrist, and as a spiritual researcher, I've been very interested
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.30,0:00:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,in the field of health and self-healing. So we'll be talking again about the relationship between
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.36,0:01:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,body, mind, and spirit, because we know from our previous talks,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.68,0:01:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that body has no way of experiencing itself, that body is experienced in mind only.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in mind that you experience the body. We know that the body expresses that which is held
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.35,0:01:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,in mind. We know that mind itself cannot really experience itself. It has to be experienced from
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.05,0:01:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,an even greater energy field, which we call consciousness. So we go from dense form,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.93,0:01:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,ever expanding into ever increasing formlessness. And so we end up with the experiencing of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,experience itself, or that field called awareness, which is beyond consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.11,0:01:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're looking today at that relationship between body, mind, and spirit, very important
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.65,0:01:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,when we're considering the whole subject of health. We'll be looking at consciousness itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.63,0:02:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,because all experience is going on within consciousness itself. And because the power,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.51,0:02:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,the power of the energy fields here, we've discovered that healing comes out of attitudes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.05,0:02:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and belief systems and that which is held in mind. And therefore, health is also coming
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.95,0:02:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,out of expressions of levels of consciousness. And to understand this and make it more understandable,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.31,0:02:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,more comprehensible, especially to people who are very logical in the orientation, which
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.86,0:02:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I was of course, being a skeptical scientist, what we've done is prepared here an integrated
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.34,0:02:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,map of consciousness based on a mathematical relationship between the energy fields. And
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.62,0:02:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy field that we've done, and myself and my coworker, Glorian Ross, over the last
