Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,those physical abnormalities actually are brought into existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.33,0:14:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The reverse side of it is when that personality leaves and how that comes about is
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.03,0:14:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,sometimes intoxication or shifts of emotionality or life circumstances, suddenly the other personality comes into the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.53,0:14:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The other personality which has no such belief, the body promptly heals itself of all those illnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.77,0:14:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now why does the mind have such power over the body?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.40,0:14:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps we can look at the physics of it a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.04,0:14:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The physics would make it very easily understandable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.32,0:14:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We sit in our calibrated system here where death is zero and guilt is 30, 50, we went all the way up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.06,0:14:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We can get the energy field of anything in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.26,0:14:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we calibrate the energy field of the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.76,0:15:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the physical body itself, and we find that the physical body is not a reversed state like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.76,0:15:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The body is not a negative state, but the energy field of the body is about 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, its power, its energy field is about 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.52,0:15:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy field of mind begins here around 400.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.32,0:15:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It runs between 400 and 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.92,0:15:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are the energy fields of the intellect, reason, logic, mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.56,0:15:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and beliefs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.75,0:15:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore if we hold a thought in mind that says,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.75,0:15:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,seeds like in a strawberry or caraway seeds or any kind of seeds give me diverticulitis,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.87,0:15:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,then the power of that thought, you see coming out of an energy field of between 400 and 500,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.41,0:15:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the body which only has an energy field of 100 is overpowered by the power of the pattern
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.75,0:15:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,of that belief.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.75,0:15:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And all thoughts have a form.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.75,0:16:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the form, which is there in the collective unconscious,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.75,0:16:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the collective consciousness, the social consciousness, whatever you want to call it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.75,0:16:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,is there in great detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.75,0:16:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The pattern of that and the coming about of how the mechanics of that would happen is already there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.75,0:16:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So if we buy into that thought, if we go into agreement with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,it's like we bring it into our own unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And that then expresses itself within the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So the body will do what the mind believes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So the healing of the body then and the achievement of health
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.10,0:16:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,is achieved not by addressing the body directly but by addressing the mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,moving right into the fields of consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So if the body is expressing that which is held in consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.10,0:16:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,then what we need to look at is what is being held in consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Very often what's being held in consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.36,0:16:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,we are not aware of.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.36,0:16:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case we call it being unconscious of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.36,0:17:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,By looking at the body we may have no recall of ever having had such a thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.06,0:17:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But the body is telling us what must be held.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.06,0:17:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like an x-ray.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.06,0:17:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The x-ray is telling us what must be held in mind for this to be presenting itself in the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.06,0:17:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So if the person, let's say, develops clinical diabetes,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.12,0:17:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and he says,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.12,0:17:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember anything in my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.12,0:17:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember anything in my family ever being said about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.12,0:17:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember anybody in my family had diabetes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.12,0:17:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see where it could have arisen in my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.73,0:17:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We know that somewhere in the unconscious is the belief in diabetes
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.73,0:17:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and all that goes with diabetes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.73,0:17:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If we do individual research with the individual patient
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.73,0:17:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,long enough and patiently enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.73,0:17:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,we will uncover where the program came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.76,0:17:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But what it tells us is that the program is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.76,0:17:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That the person thinks, I am subject to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.76,0:17:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore the healing has to be of the belief system.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:18:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to heal where the origin of the illness starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.76,0:18:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And so health comes out of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.76,0:18:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes out of positive mental attitudes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.76,0:18:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes out of a field of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.76,0:18:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes out of a level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.76,0:18:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,which expresses itself on the lower plane, the physical plane,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.76,0:18:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,as an expression of health coming out of these fields above neutral.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.76,0:18:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of willingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.76,0:18:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the willingness to be accepting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.76,0:18:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of lovingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.76,0:18:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of inner joyfulness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.76,0:18:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And out of an inner state of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.76,0:18:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is mental was in the 400s.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.76,0:18:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And that love is 500s.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course spirit is 600 and above.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually spirit begins here once the needle moves to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.76,0:18:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It becomes increasingly consciously aware that it is spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.15,0:18:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So therefore the intellect is not man's highest faculty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.15,0:18:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Contrary to the age of reason and other learned works.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:19:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Or those intellectuals who hold the thing that differentiates man from the animal is his intellect.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.18,0:19:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The intellect is only in the 400s.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.18,0:19:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There is something beyond mind, beyond logic, beyond reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.18,0:19:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,which jumps and transcends into a whole different paradigm,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.18,0:19:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,a whole different way of being.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.18,0:19:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's necessary to know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.18,0:19:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's necessary to know then that which heals,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,which is here on up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.31,0:19:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's necessary to look at the contribution that is coming into an illness from these various levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.40,0:19:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We find that always with an illness,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,if we now understand illness,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,then we will understand its reverse,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,which is health.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.40,0:19:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That in illness there is always unconscious guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.40,0:19:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Never has there been an illness without unconscious guilt in our research.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.78,0:19:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There is an unconscious guilt and therefore the undoing of unconscious guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.78,0:19:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not talking about conscious guilt now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.78,0:19:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We're talking about unconscious guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.78,0:20:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore there are whole systems of how to let go of unconscious guilt
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.78,0:20:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,through the process of the willingness to forgive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.78,0:20:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Moving from here then,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.78,0:20:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,meaning the willingness to let go of judgment,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.78,0:20:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,of criticism and judgment,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.78,0:20:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the willingness to let go of make wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.78,0:20:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,of right wrong as an orientation towards life,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.78,0:20:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and a willingness to move towards a forgivingness
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.78,0:20:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and the desire to understand life out of compassion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.78,0:20:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So moving out of the contribution of guilt
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.26,0:20:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and all the negative emotions,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.26,0:20:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and we move up to the mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.26,0:20:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,we find that illness requires several things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.26,0:20:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It requires unconscious guilt
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and it requires a mental belief system.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.26,0:20:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind has to believe in a certain belief
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,for the person to believe that they are subject to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.26,0:20:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as though unconscious guilt
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.26,0:20:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,looks for something to justify itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.26,0:20:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So it can be any illness out there
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.26,0:21:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and we see that after a certain illness
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.26,0:21:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,gets popularized on television,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.26,0:21:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,let's say some celebrity,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,shares with us that particular illness
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.26,0:21:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's followed by an epidemic of that illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.26,0:21:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of suggestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.90,0:21:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind now buys that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.90,0:21:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind buys the belief system
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.90,0:21:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,in the specificity of a particular disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.90,0:21:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Unconscious guilt gives us
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.90,0:21:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and gives it the power.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.32,0:21:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the unconscious guilt
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.32,0:21:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,looking for an expression
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.32,0:21:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,through the autonomic nervous system
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.32,0:21:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and through the hormonal system
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.32,0:21:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and through all the stress mechanisms within the body
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.32,0:21:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and through the acupuncture energy system.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.32,0:21:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Which brings us to the subject of kinesiology
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,which we mentioned in one of our other talks
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.48,0:21:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,as a way of checking out for yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.48,0:21:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,these calibrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.48,0:21:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you who are familiar with kinesiology
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.48,0:21:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,know how it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.48,0:21:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who aren't,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.48,0:21:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I can just briefly explain it to you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.48,0:21:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,in about less than a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.48,0:22:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What you do is you press down
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.15,0:22:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and you have somebody hold out their arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.15,0:22:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You look away from them
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.15,0:22:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and you press down and ask them to resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.15,0:22:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you ask them to hold something negative in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.15,0:22:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Something about in their life
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.15,0:22:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,over which they have grief or fear
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.15,0:22:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,or somebody they hate, let's say.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.15,0:22:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And as you press,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.15,0:22:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,now you ask them to resist
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.15,0:22:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and you press down again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.15,0:22:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and you'll see instantly the whole body goes weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.15,0:22:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The body goes weak
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.15,0:22:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,figuratively and symbolically
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.15,0:22:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,it goes weak on many levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.15,0:22:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Now if we ask the same person
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.18,0:22:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to forget that and instead
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.18,0:22:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to hold in mind something or someone they love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.18,0:22:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and we press down again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.18,0:22:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll find that with all our strength
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.18,0:22:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,we can't push their arm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.18,0:22:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They are amazingly strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.18,0:22:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The brain hemispheres are synchronized,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.18,0:22:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the acupuncture energy system is balanced
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.18,0:22:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and the energy flow of health,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.18,0:22:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy of life is flowing correctly
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.18,0:22:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,down all the energy channels
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.18,0:22:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and energizing all the organs of the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.18,0:22:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So that we see every time we hold a negative thought
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.18,0:23:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,then the energy flow down one of the 12 main meridians
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.18,0:23:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,is interrupted.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.18,0:23:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we habitually blow certain acupuncture meridians
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.18,0:23:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,then disease comes about in that organ.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.18,0:23:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So we see that any of these negative emotions
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.56,0:23:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,is the direct cause of a disease process.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.56,0:23:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Unconscious guilt gives it enormous power
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.56,0:23:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and the form that that illness takes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.56,0:23:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,then is coming from mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.56,0:23:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,what the mind believes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.56,0:23:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So what the mind believes is what the body expresses.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.69,0:23:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to look at how experience is experienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.72,0:23:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We see that the body in and of itself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.72,0:23:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,as we have said in other of these talks,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.72,0:23:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the body in and of itself is in ascension,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.72,0:23:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,as curious as that may sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.76,0:23:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It has no capacity to experience itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.76,0:23:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The experience, the next level of experience
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.76,0:23:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,is coming through sensations
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.76,0:23:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,coming from the senses of the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.76,0:23:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So we don't experience the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.76,0:24:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,we experience the senses of the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.14,0:24:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Senses themselves have no capacity
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.14,0:24:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to experience themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.65,0:24:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They're experienced in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.65,0:24:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.65,0:24:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,it's in mind that we experience the senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.65,0:24:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And the senses then report what's going on
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.65,0:24:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,within the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.65,0:24:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're already several levels removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.13,0:24:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind itself isn't able to experience
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.13,0:24:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,its own experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.13,0:24:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to be in a greater, larger energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.13,0:24:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,than itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.13,0:24:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And in this case it is the energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.13,0:24:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.13,0:24:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It is because of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.13,0:24:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that we're aware of what is going on in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.13,0:24:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind then is telling us via the senses
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.13,0:24:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,what is going on in body.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.13,0:24:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see that which we are,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.13,0:24:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,when I say I, me,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.13,0:24:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,is already several levels removed
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.23,0:24:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,from the physical body.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.23,0:24:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness itself requires
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.80,0:24:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,something greater than itself
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.80,0:24:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and that we call awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.80,0:24:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.80,0:25:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Awareness is what allows us to know
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.25,0:25:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,what is going on in consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.25,0:25:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,reporting what is happening within mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.25,0:25:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,which in turn is reporting what is happening
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.25,0:25:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,via the senses about the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.25,0:25:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is essentially myself then
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.50,0:25:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,is many levels removed from the physical body.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.50,0:25:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's necessary for us to look at it
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.85,0:25:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and get that correctly in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.85,0:25:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,because now we see that it's the mind
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.85,0:25:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,that has power over the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.85,0:25:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We saw the physics of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.85,0:25:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,that the energy fields of the 400s
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.85,0:25:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,just by their sheer power
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.85,0:25:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,are greater than that of the physical body.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.85,0:25:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The physical body does
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.85,0:25:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,what the mind tells it to do
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.85,0:25:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore if the mind says
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.85,0:25:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I have this disease or that disease
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.85,0:25:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the body complies.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.85,0:25:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,When we look at this we see the importance then
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.85,0:25:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,of not buying into
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.85,0:25:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,programs
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.85,0:25:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and all of which are really
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.85,0:25:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,limitations of the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.95,0:25:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We see the importance of consciously
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.95,0:26:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,cancelling and saying
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.95,0:26:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,something which is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.95,0:26:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.95,0:26:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I am an infinite being
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.87,0:26:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,not subject to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.87,0:26:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So when we hear something
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.00,0:26:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,like eggs which are
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.00,0:26:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,full of cholesterol and their
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.00,0:26:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,cholesterol will give you heart disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.00,0:26:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If you buy into the thought form,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.44,0:26:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,if you buy into that belief system
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.44,0:26:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that eggs, cholesterol
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.44,0:26:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,will give me heart disease
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.44,0:26:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,raise my blood cholesterol
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.44,0:26:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,what happens is that the body
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.44,0:26:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,agrees and
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.44,0:26:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,when you eat cholesterol
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.44,0:26:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,what happens is your blood cholesterol goes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.44,0:26:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You can experiment with this
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.21,0:26:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,because I've done it
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.21,0:26:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and at one time I had a very high cholesterol
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.40,0:26:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and I began to cancel the belief system.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.40,0:26:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I kept saying I'm an infinite being
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.40,0:26:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not subject to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.40,0:26:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm only subject to what I hold in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.44,0:26:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This does not apply to me
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.44,0:26:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and I hereby cancel it and refuse it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.44,0:27:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well if the mind
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.60,0:27:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,can empower you with a
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.60,0:27:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,negative belief system it can reverse itself
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.60,0:27:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,can it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.60,0:27:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore you begin telling yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.60,0:27:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that they have no effect on me
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.60,0:27:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that that's only a belief system
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.60,0:27:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that I don't have to buy into that
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.60,0:27:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to go into agreement with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.66,0:27:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,When I go into agreement with it
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.66,0:27:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I give it the power of the collective
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.66,0:27:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,energy of that belief.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.66,0:27:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,When I refuse it
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.66,0:27:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,then I release myself from the collective
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.66,0:27:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,energy of that belief system.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.66,0:27:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I count myself out.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.85,0:27:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So one attitude then
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.85,0:27:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,is to not buy into
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.85,0:27:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,agreement
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.85,0:27:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,with negative belief systems
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.85,0:27:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,having to do with your health.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.85,0:27:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This is very important
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.85,0:27:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,when it comes to epidemics
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.85,0:27:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the hysteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.85,0:27:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see the programming that comes in
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.85,0:27:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,is aided and abetted by
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.85,0:27:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,an emotional program.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.85,0:27:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So now we hear much about AIDS
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.04,0:27:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,let's say.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.04,0:28:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we hear about
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.04,0:28:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,constant repetition in the media
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.04,0:28:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,who play upon what?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.04,0:28:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.04,0:28:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.04,0:28:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Anger about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.04,0:28:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course guilt about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.04,0:28:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What better disease to bring up all
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.04,0:28:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,man's feelings of sinfulness
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.04,0:28:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and guilt especially about his sexuality
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.04,0:28:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,which is so common in our culture
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.04,0:28:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,in all cultures.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.68,0:28:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is the highest expression
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.68,0:28:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,of love of course
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.68,0:28:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,when it takes on a negative
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.68,0:28:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and when it is turned over
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.68,0:28:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes the lowest.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.68,0:28:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore what a better area
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.68,0:28:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,in which to create an epidemic
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.68,0:28:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,through sheer belief in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.68,0:28:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The unconscious guilt
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.68,0:28:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,not to mention the conscious guilt
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.68,0:28:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,about one's sexuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.68,0:28:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The sadness about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.68,0:28:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The grief over that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.68,0:28:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The fear about the disease etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.68,0:28:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All of this contributing then
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.68,0:28:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and setting the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.68,0:28:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So you have the mental belief system
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.68,0:28:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,coming out of an energy field in the 400's.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.68,0:29:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You have fear about it
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.68,0:29:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,coming out of a negative 100's.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.68,0:29:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And you have the guilt coming out
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.68,0:29:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,of the minus 30's.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.68,0:29:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And so you have the exact set up for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.68,0:29:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The exact set up
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.68,0:29:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,because the mind will choose
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.68,0:29:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that which
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.68,0:29:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,it is impressed with.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.68,0:29:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And will use that
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.68,0:29:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,as a form of expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.68,0:29:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,In the case of the cholesterol
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.68,0:29:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the experiment I did with that
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.81,0:29:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,with my own self
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.81,0:29:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,was to cancel the thought
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.81,0:29:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.13,0:29:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And as time went by
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.13,0:29:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,in fact it didn't take very long
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.13,0:29:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,with that particular thing
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.13,0:29:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the cholesterol level came down
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.13,0:29:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and now I can eat 3 eggs for breakfast
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.13,0:29:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,every single morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.13,0:29:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots of cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.13,0:29:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact I live on a high cholesterol diet
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.13,0:29:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and yet my cholesterol is low
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.13,0:29:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and sometimes even below normal
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.12,0:29:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,for my age.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.12,0:29:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The body will do exactly
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.12,0:29:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,what the mind believes
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.12,0:30:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's my belief in that
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.12,0:30:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,make it happen within my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.70,0:30:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of the nature
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.70,0:30:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,of the unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.70,0:30:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It creates the opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.89,0:30:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,for that to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.89,0:30:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We certainly see that in accidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.89,0:30:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The person is so called accident prone
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.89,0:30:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the form that is taken
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.89,0:30:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,in that person's mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.89,0:30:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Unconsciously they just manage
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.89,0:30:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,to get their body in the right place
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.89,0:30:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,at the right time.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.89,0:30:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Just to get hit by the fender of the car
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.08,0:30:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,slip down the stairs, get hit on the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.08,0:30:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind will find a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.08,0:30:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,People will just slip into
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.08,0:30:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,sort of a hypnotic trance
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.08,0:30:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and expose themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.31,0:30:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,to the correct opportunities
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.31,0:30:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to make that manifest within their life.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.44,0:30:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance with the cold virus
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.44,0:30:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,there's many experiments
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.44,0:30:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,where we take 100 subject volunteers
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.44,0:30:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and expose them to a very heavy dose
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.44,0:30:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,of cold virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.44,0:30:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We see what happens
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.44,0:30:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,is that not everybody gets the cold virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.44,0:30:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Only a certain percentage
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.44,0:30:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,will always get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.44,0:31:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words if the power
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.50,0:31:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,was in the virus rather than
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.50,0:31:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,within consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.50,0:31:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,all 100 would get it
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.50,0:31:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,because that virus would be so potent.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.50,0:31:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually what happens is
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.50,0:31:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe only 65%
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.50,0:31:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,will get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.50,0:31:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A third don't believe in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.50,0:31:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There's sufficient doubt within the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.50,0:31:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There's insufficient unconscious guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.50,0:31:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not acceptable to the person
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.50,0:31:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,to express it in that form.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.50,0:31:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing is universal.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.50,0:31:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We see the same thing with healings.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.50,0:31:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Penicillin doesn't cure 100%
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.50,0:31:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,of pneumonias.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.50,0:31:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It only cures a certain percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.50,0:31:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Every medical treatment
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.50,0:31:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,has only a certain percentage
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.50,0:31:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,of people who will respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.50,0:31:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And what is the difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.50,0:31:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It is because the others
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.50,0:31:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,don't have sufficient unconscious guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.50,0:31:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not operative.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.50,0:31:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This particular illness doesn't fit
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.50,0:31:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,any particular thought form
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.50,0:31:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that they have bought into.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.50,0:31:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And so both sides of it
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.50,0:31:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,are the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.50,0:32:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy that we put into
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.98,0:32:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,a certain belief system.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.98,0:32:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So we see then that health
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.98,0:32:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is the willingness to let go
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.98,0:32:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,of buying into negativity.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.98,0:32:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should a person buy into negativity anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.98,0:32:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it that some people
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.98,0:32:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,are so programmable?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.98,0:32:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We know people that go into hysteria
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.98,0:32:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,every time they open a magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.98,0:32:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The latest illness sends them into a panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.98,0:32:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And it has to do then
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.98,0:32:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,with the amount of fear
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.98,0:32:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and the amount of guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.98,0:32:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as though the person
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.98,0:32:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,knows what to be afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.98,0:32:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as though they're only too aware
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.98,0:32:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,that because they have so much of this
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.98,0:32:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,for them to even hear about it
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.98,0:32:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and become mentally programmed
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.98,0:32:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is almost enough to make it happen
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.98,0:32:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,in their life.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.08,0:32:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So what does this tell us then
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.08,0:32:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,about the steps towards optimal health?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.08,0:32:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It means the willingness
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.08,0:32:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,to adopt mental attitudes
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.08,0:32:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,that are positive and constructive.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.08,0:32:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And this means the willingness
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.08,0:32:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,to let go of the negative ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.08,0:33:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The willingness to take an easy going
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.08,0:33:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,forgiving attitude towards life.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.08,0:33:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The unwillingness
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.08,0:33:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,to buy into negative programming.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.08,0:33:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The owning
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.08,0:33:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,of the power of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.08,0:33:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, going into denial
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.08,0:33:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,going into denial
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.46,0:33:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and blaming it
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.46,0:33:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,on out there
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.46,0:33:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,is giving your power away.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.52,0:33:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We see that these energy fields below courage
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.52,0:33:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,here are all levels in which the person
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.52,0:33:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,has become victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.52,0:33:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happened is they've given
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.52,0:33:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,their power away
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.52,0:33:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and put it on something outside of themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.52,0:33:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And these people
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.52,0:33:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,in these levels here have said
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.52,0:33:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to themselves unconsciously
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.52,0:33:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the source of my happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.52,0:33:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,is outside of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.52,0:33:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They've put their survival on something
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.52,0:33:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,outside of themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.52,0:33:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,As we move into levels of truth
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.52,0:33:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,above the levels of courage
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.52,0:33:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and the energy fields are now going positive
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.52,0:33:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,we see that the person
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.52,0:33:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,is reowning their power.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.52,0:33:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The person is saying, I and I alone
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.52,0:34:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,have the power to create
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.52,0:34:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,happiness and opportunity in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.52,0:34:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It is coming from within me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.52,0:34:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And so these people
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.52,0:34:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,then own that health
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.52,0:34:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,is something that comes
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.52,0:34:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,from within.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.52,0:34:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,These people are coming from
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.52,0:34:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the victim of disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.52,0:34:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, we are not the victim of viruses.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.52,0:34:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not the victim of accidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.52,0:34:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not the victim of cholesterol.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.52,0:34:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not the victim of uric acid levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.52,0:34:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not the victim of those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.52,0:34:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,When we reown our own power
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.52,0:34:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,we say, hey, it's my mind
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.62,0:34:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that's been creating that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.62,0:34:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,My mind believes that eating liver
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.62,0:34:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and kidneys is going to give you
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.62,0:34:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,a high uric acid level
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.62,0:34:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's going to give you an attack of gout.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.04,0:34:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My mind is so powerful
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.04,0:34:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that if I believe that
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.04,0:34:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,it will literally make it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.36,0:34:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a hard thing for many people to accept
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.36,0:34:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that their mind has that much power.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.36,0:34:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean to tell me that if I believe
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.36,0:34:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that eating sugar and sweets
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.36,0:34:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,is going to give me hypoglycemia
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.36,0:34:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that that will give me hypoglycemia?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.36,0:35:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed it will.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.36,0:35:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we go back to the physics involved
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.36,0:35:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and we remind ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.36,0:35:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that the body's energy field of 100
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.36,0:35:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,is weak compared to the belief systems of 400.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.36,0:35:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The belief that sugar and sweets
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.36,0:35:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,will give me hypoglycemia
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.36,0:35:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,or give me diabetes
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.36,0:35:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,or give me overweight.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.68,0:35:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Those belief systems are sufficient to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.68,0:35:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And all the explanations
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.68,0:35:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that we come upon
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.68,0:35:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the rationalizations
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.68,0:35:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that justify that we are the victim of that
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.68,0:35:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,are just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.68,0:35:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.68,0:35:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They're substituting an explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.68,0:35:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that it's scientific
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.12,0:35:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,is still an explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.12,0:35:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The science of it
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.12,0:35:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,is the mechanism.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.12,0:35:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The description of the mechanism
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.12,0:35:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,of how this comes about on the physical plane
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.12,0:35:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,is only a description
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.12,0:35:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,of the mechanism.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.12,0:35:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not a description of cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.12,0:35:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Cause is on the level of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.12,0:35:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Effect is on the level of body.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.12,0:35:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the other way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.12,0:36:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we really just merely reverse
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.12,0:36:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,that understanding,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.12,0:36:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,we have the whole key to health and healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.12,0:36:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Health then comes out of a positive
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.12,0:36:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,mental attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.12,0:36:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a thing we've heard many times, haven't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.12,0:36:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, many people are annoyed by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.12,0:36:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, because that infers if I have a sickness
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.12,0:36:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a positive mental attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.12,0:36:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's look at mental attitude then.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.22,0:36:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's look at what is meant by that
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.22,0:36:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and the part that that plays in
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.22,0:36:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,health and freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.22,0:36:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,from sickness and suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.28,0:36:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We said the one thing that goes on
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.28,0:36:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,in the unhealthy person is
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.28,0:36:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,this unconscious guilt
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.28,0:36:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and the cure for that
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.28,0:36:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,is the willingness to be forgiving,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.28,0:36:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,to actually take courses in forgiveness
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.28,0:36:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,if that is necessary,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.28,0:36:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,such as the Course in Miracles,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.28,0:36:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,which is specifically designed
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.28,0:36:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,to let go of that tendency of the mind
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.28,0:36:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,to criticize, to attack, and to judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.35,0:36:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The willingness then
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.35,0:36:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to let go judgmentalism.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.38,0:36:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the mechanism is unconscious,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.38,0:36:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,so the person may not see
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.38,0:36:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the connection between
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.38,0:37:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the fact that their mind is critical
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.38,0:37:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and judgmental.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.38,0:37:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If your mind is critical and judgmental
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.38,0:37:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,of others, of course it is critical
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.38,0:37:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and judgmental of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.38,0:37:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The creation of the unconscious guilt
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.38,0:37:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,then builds up a certain energy
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.38,0:37:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,which expresses itself through
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.38,0:37:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the autonomic nervous system
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.38,0:37:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and the acupuncture energy system.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.38,0:37:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So that is the cure of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.38,0:37:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The contribution from mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.38,0:37:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the belief system,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.38,0:37:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,we said is the power of refusal,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.83,0:37:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,to deny it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.83,0:37:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It is your power now
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.83,0:37:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,that it is the mind and the mind itself
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.83,0:37:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,that is the cause of the illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.83,0:37:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The willingness to give up
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.83,0:37:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,the position of victim,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.83,0:37:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,the willingness to reown one's own power
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.83,0:37:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,is part and parcel of the third thing
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.83,0:37:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,that is necessary for health,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.83,0:37:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and that is one's overall
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.83,0:37:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual growth and development.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.83,0:37:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The overall moving out of
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.83,0:37:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,these negative energy patterns,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.83,0:37:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,the willingness to face truths
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.83,0:37:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,within ourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.83,0:37:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and the moving into a positive energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.37,0:38:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This can be done actually rather rapidly.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.37,0:38:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.37,0:38:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Because willingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.37,0:38:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,you see, is the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.37,0:38:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Through the willingness to look at it,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.37,0:38:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,the willingness to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.37,0:38:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,well, I don't really believe this,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.37,0:38:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,but it is said that my mind has the power
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.37,0:38:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,to create an illness within my body,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.37,0:38:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and so I am willing to look at that
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.37,0:38:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,because I have an open mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.37,0:38:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an open mind
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.37,0:38:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and I am willing to agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.37,0:38:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,My intention aligns then
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.47,0:38:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and I begin to move into accepting
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.47,0:38:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,which I discover.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.47,0:38:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I begin to find
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.47,0:38:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,that moving into lovingness
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.47,0:38:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,has a curative and healing power.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.47,0:38:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And how do we do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.47,0:38:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Our willingness to forgive,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.47,0:38:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,our willingness here moves us
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.47,0:38:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,right into the willingness to forgive,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.47,0:38:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and if we
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.47,0:38:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,can quickly move ourself into
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.47,0:38:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,the willingness to be compassionate.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.47,0:38:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What does compassion mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.17,0:38:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Compassion means
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.40,0:38:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the willingness to see the innocence
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.40,0:39:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,within all things.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.40,0:39:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, that coincides
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.40,0:39:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,with the willingness to forgive.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.40,0:39:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of compassion
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.40,0:39:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,comes the power,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.40,0:39:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the capacity,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.40,0:39:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,coming out of our intention
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.40,0:39:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,to really see into the hearts of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.40,0:39:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,When we see into the hearts of others,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.40,0:39:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,as we've said in other talks,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.40,0:39:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,what we discover is the innocence
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.40,0:39:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,of the child
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.40,0:39:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,within each and every one of us
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.40,0:39:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,because it is intrinsic to the nature
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.40,0:39:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.43,0:39:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,is that intrinsic innocence
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.43,0:39:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,which never dies
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.43,0:39:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter how long we live.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.43,0:39:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The innocence of the child
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.43,0:39:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,is what bought the mistake,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.43,0:39:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,which bought the negative program
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.43,0:39:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.43,0:39:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The being aware,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.43,0:39:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,that that intrinsic innocence of the child
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.43,0:39:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,is ever with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.43,0:39:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the innocence of the child
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.43,0:39:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that sits there in front of the television set
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.00,0:39:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and buys the negative programming.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.00,0:39:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of its naivete,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.00,0:39:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,out of its lack of discernment,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.00,0:40:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the innocence of the child
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.00,0:40:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,says,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.00,0:40:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,this is a world
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.00,0:40:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that is out to program you
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.00,0:40:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,with as much negativity
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.00,0:40:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,as you're willing to buy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.20,0:40:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, it gets well paid to do that
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.20,0:40:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,because advertising is usually based
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.20,0:40:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,in playing off of these negative energy fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.20,0:40:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,All of our fears,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.20,0:40:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,all of our desires,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.20,0:40:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,all of our pridefulness,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.20,0:40:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,all of it as you see below the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.20,0:40:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The willingness then
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.20,0:40:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,to be aware
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.20,0:40:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,that within us is our innocence
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.20,0:40:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and that the innocence
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.20,0:40:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,needs to be protected.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.20,0:40:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So we come into what's called self-care.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.20,0:40:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Self-care,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.20,0:40:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the capacity to love oneself now,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.20,0:40:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,means taking responsibility
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.20,0:40:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,to protect ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.20,0:40:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,from that innocence
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.20,0:40:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and the willingness
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.20,0:40:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,to undo the mistakes
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.20,0:40:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,that the mind picked up
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.20,0:40:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,as a result of its innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.20,0:40:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We can handle now
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.23,0:40:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,looking at ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.23,0:41:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and healing that which we find within us
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.23,0:41:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,if we're coming from the compassion
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.23,0:41:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,of the awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.23,0:41:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,of the intrinsic innocence
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.23,0:41:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,of our consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.26,0:41:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We see that it was innocence
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.26,0:41:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that got programmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.26,0:41:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we take responsibility for that
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.26,0:41:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and we say, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.26,0:41:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,in my innocence I bought all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.26,0:41:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,In my innocence I didn't know any better.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.26,0:41:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,In my innocence I thought
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.26,0:41:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that the right thing to do
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.26,0:41:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,was to be judgmental,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.26,0:41:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,to condemn people,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.26,0:41:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,to judge them as right and wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.26,0:41:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.80,0:41:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We have amongst our acquaintances
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.80,0:41:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and the people that we've done research
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.80,0:41:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,with people
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.28,0:41:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,who have had every disease known to mankind,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.28,0:41:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,advanced multiple sclerosis,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.28,0:41:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,cancers of all kinds,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.28,0:41:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,all kinds of advanced illnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.28,0:41:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And these people
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.28,0:41:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,merely were willing
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.28,0:41:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,to look into this question.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.28,0:41:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And when they did,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.28,0:41:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,they went through the processes
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.28,0:42:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that we've described in this talk
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.28,0:42:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and they all came out
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.28,0:42:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,of their illnesses
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.28,0:42:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,without any residuals whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.24,0:42:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This capacity then
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.24,0:42:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,to be forgiving is within us,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.24,0:42:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the capacity for compassion.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.24,0:42:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of it comes
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.24,0:42:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,a general attitude,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.24,0:42:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,a way in which we look at ourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.24,0:42:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So from our bigness,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.24,0:42:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,from our greatness,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.24,0:42:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,we look at our humanness
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.24,0:42:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,through forgiving eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.24,0:42:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and we begin to forgive ourself
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.24,0:42:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,for all the things
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.24,0:42:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,that were limitations
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.24,0:42:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,of the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.24,0:42:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All of these things
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.24,0:42:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,with an energy fuel
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.24,0:42:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,with the arrows going to the left
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.24,0:42:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,are denials of the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.24,0:42:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All of those with an arrow
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.24,0:42:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,going to the right
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.72,0:42:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,is the acceptance of that
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.72,0:42:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,which is true and positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.72,0:42:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And so health,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.72,0:42:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,because the body is reflecting
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.72,0:42:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,what the mind believes
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.72,0:42:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and the mind is reflecting
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.72,0:43:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,our spiritual position.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.72,0:43:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Spirit has the greatest power of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.72,0:43:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It is willing to accept
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.72,0:43:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the power of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.72,0:43:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we have to be attentive
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.72,0:43:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and we have to persevere
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.72,0:43:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and we can't let it get away
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.72,0:43:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,with expressing negativity
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.72,0:43:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,without stopping it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.72,0:43:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So we get to develop
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.72,0:43:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,sort of an ear for negativity
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.72,0:43:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and begin to recognize it
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.68,0:43:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,for what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.84,0:43:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We let go of false humility
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.84,0:43:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and we start questioning
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.91,0:43:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,such remarks as,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.91,0:43:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,oh, my handwriting is poor
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.91,0:43:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,or I gain weight
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.91,0:43:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,in the same amount of food
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.91,0:43:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,that other people stay thin.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.91,0:43:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The minute we hear ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.91,0:43:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,saying these limiting,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.91,0:43:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,self-defeating, self-attacking thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.91,0:43:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,they have to be stopped and canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.91,0:43:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The handwriting is poor
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.91,0:43:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,because there's a belief system
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.91,0:43:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,that I have poor handwriting
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.07,0:43:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and not vice versa.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.07,0:43:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So what we're doing then
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.07,0:44:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,is reversing the whole programming
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.07,0:44:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,of the mind as far as
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.10,0:44:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,we're coming back to a principle
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.10,0:44:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,which you can demonstrate
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.10,0:44:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,through your own experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.32,0:44:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That the physical is the expression
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.32,0:44:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,of the mental and not vice versa.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.32,0:44:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't that we came to the conclusion
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.32,0:44:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,our handwriting is poor
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.32,0:44:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,because our handwriting is poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.32,0:44:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The handwriting is poor
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.32,0:44:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,because the cause was in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.32,0:44:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The belief system.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.32,0:44:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps a remark
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.32,0:44:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,picked up in childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.32,0:44:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody says your handwriting is poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.32,0:44:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,From that point on that program
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.32,0:44:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,we have to look at the ingenuity
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.87,0:44:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,of the unconscious mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.87,0:44:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,To really see it
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.06,0:44:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,it would be great if you had
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.06,0:44:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,some experience in watching
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.06,0:44:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,hypnotic experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.06,0:44:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if we tell the person
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.06,0:44:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,that when they wake up
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.06,0:44:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,their legs will be itching
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.06,0:44:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and then we induce amnesia
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.06,0:44:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,for that suggestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.06,0:44:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,When we wake the person up
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.06,0:45:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll say how do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.06,0:45:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Instantly the mind will start
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.06,0:45:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,creating the most marvelous
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.06,0:45:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,things.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.06,0:45:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The person doesn't just say
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.06,0:45:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,well my legs itch.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.06,0:45:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind always gets in there
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.06,0:45:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,in a creative way
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.06,0:45:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and will say and start explaining
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.06,0:45:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,well I've got wool pants on
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.06,0:45:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and you know I'm allergic to wool
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.06,0:45:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and the heat in this room
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.06,0:45:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and steam heat always creates that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.06,0:45:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just marvelous to listen
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.06,0:45:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,to the inventiveness of the mind
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.06,0:45:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,as it begins to create
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.06,0:45:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the reasons for the symptom
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.06,0:45:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind will do the same thing then
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.44,0:45:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's helpful to look at ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.44,0:45:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,as though we've been hypnotized
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.44,0:45:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,subjects half of our life
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.44,0:45:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and didn't even realize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.44,0:45:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What is hypnosis?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.44,0:45:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's suggestibility is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.44,0:45:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It means to be in an unguarded
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.44,0:45:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,suggestible relaxed state.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.44,0:45:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So anytime you've been
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.44,0:45:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,in an unguarded relaxed
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.44,0:45:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,suggestible state
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.44,0:45:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you've picked up all the programming
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.44,0:46:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and whether you remember it or not
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.44,0:46:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,it is still operative.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.44,0:46:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Half asleep as you sat in front
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.44,0:46:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,of the television set
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.44,0:46:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,hour after hour after hour
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.44,0:46:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,of programming went into the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.44,0:46:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,These are all now
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.44,0:46:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,unconscious
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.44,0:46:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,hypnotic programs.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.48,0:46:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we discover what we've been programmed?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.48,0:46:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,With is by watching
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.48,0:46:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,to see what comes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.48,0:46:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So the idea oh I'm no good
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.48,0:46:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.15,0:46:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I never was very good at playing cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.15,0:46:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have the belief system
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.15,0:46:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're not very good at playing cards
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.15,0:46:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not going to operate in your life
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.15,0:46:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,is that you're not going to be very good
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.15,0:46:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,at playing cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.15,0:46:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That goes back then to reinforce
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.15,0:46:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the belief system.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.15,0:46:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And so these belief systems
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.15,0:46:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,become self reinforcing.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.15,0:46:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They become self fulfilling prophecies.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.15,0:46:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We hold the belief unwittingly
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.15,0:46:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,it then manifests in our life
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.15,0:46:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,we look at that and we say see
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.47,0:46:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and that justifies the belief system.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.47,0:46:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So by looking at our life
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.47,0:47:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,we can tell what beliefs we are holding
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.47,0:47:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,if we can't recall them
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.47,0:47:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore our movement
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.47,0:47:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,is upward in consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.47,0:47:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,we said health is the automatic
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.47,0:47:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,expression of these energy fields up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.47,0:47:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy field of 540 and over
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.47,0:47:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,which is one of gratitude
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.47,0:47:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.47,0:47:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We see that gratitude is at 540
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.47,0:47:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,forgiveness is at 540
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.47,0:47:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and healing
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.47,0:47:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,is at 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.47,0:47:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The willingness to be forgiving
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.47,0:47:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and grateful in itself
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.47,0:47:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,automatically begins to heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.47,0:47:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Becoming a
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.46,0:47:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,loving being.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.46,0:47:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This energy field of love
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.46,0:47:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and we must talk about what that means.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.46,0:47:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't talk about
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.46,0:47:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not sentimentality.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.46,0:47:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What the world calls love
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.46,0:47:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is coming out in an energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.46,0:47:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.46,0:47:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's talking about dependency
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.46,0:47:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,it's talking about control
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.46,0:47:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,it's talking about sentimentalism
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.46,0:47:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and emotionalism
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.46,0:48:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and emotional sentimental attachment
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.46,0:48:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,in which there is
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.46,0:48:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,control going back and forth
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.46,0:48:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and the satisfaction of desiringness
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.46,0:48:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,on both sides
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.46,0:48:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is called love.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.46,0:48:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hollywood version.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.75,0:48:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,When you hear somebody say
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.75,0:48:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to love George but I don't anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.75,0:48:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,what it means is that
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.75,0:48:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,they never did love George.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.75,0:48:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What it means is they had a sentimental attachment
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.75,0:48:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,sort of a solar plexus
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.75,0:48:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,kind of a hanging onto
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.75,0:48:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,which the person then
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.75,0:48:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,romanticized and glamorized
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.75,0:48:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,within their life
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.75,0:48:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and poured a lot of emotional energy
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.75,0:48:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,into their life
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.75,0:48:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and when that was broken
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.88,0:48:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,up came a lot of negative emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.88,0:48:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind of love we're talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.88,0:48:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is unconditional love.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.88,0:48:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Unconditional love.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.97,0:48:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What is unconditional love?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.97,0:48:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an inner decision
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.97,0:48:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,that we make within ourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.97,0:48:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,See the intention
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.97,0:48:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,it's coming out of the intention
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.97,0:48:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and the decision
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.97,0:49:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,to be a loving person.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.97,0:49:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So if I decide to love you
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.97,0:49:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,that is my inner decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.97,0:49:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore I'm not the victim
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.97,0:49:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,of what goes on in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.97,0:49:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,because my decision to love
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.97,0:49:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,creates a stable energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.97,0:49:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,of unconditionality.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.97,0:49:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So the other person's behavior
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.97,0:49:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,may not please me
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.97,0:49:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,may not contribute
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.97,0:49:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,to what I desire
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.26,0:49:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,but it doesn't change the lovingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.26,0:49:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So the mother
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.26,0:49:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,for instance who visits her son in prison
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.26,0:49:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,for 20 years
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.26,0:49:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the son who is a murderer
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.26,0:49:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,loves the beingness
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.26,0:49:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the is-ness
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.26,0:49:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that which the person really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.26,0:49:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course his behavior
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.26,0:49:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,does not make her happy
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.26,0:49:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,but the love is unconditional
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.26,0:49:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter what he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.26,0:49:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So the closest to it
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.26,0:49:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that we see in our world
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.26,0:49:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,is the lovingness of the mother
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.26,0:49:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,which is unconditional.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.26,0:49:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The lovingness of 12 step groups
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.26,0:49:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,such as Alcoholics Anonymous
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.26,0:50:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,which I've used as an example
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.26,0:50:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,in other talks.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.74,0:50:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The unconditionality of that lovingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.74,0:50:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not concerned with what you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.74,0:50:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not concerned with what you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.74,0:50:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The people at the bottom here
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.74,0:50:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,are very concerned with havingness
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.74,0:50:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and rate people back and forth
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.74,0:50:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,on what they have.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.74,0:50:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,In the middle of the box
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.74,0:50:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,people are preoccupied with doingness
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.74,0:50:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and people are rated
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.74,0:50:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and their status depends on what you do
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.74,0:50:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and all the titles that go
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.74,0:50:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,with your doingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.74,0:50:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,As you move towards the top of the box
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.74,0:50:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,what people are concerned with
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.74,0:50:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,is what you are, what you have become
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.74,0:50:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,what you are beingness
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.03,0:50:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,that which you truly are.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.03,0:50:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We're concerned there
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.03,0:50:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,with a person's status
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.03,0:50:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,their value there
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.03,0:50:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,is the kind of a person that you are
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.03,0:50:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,that which you have become
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.03,0:50:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,you have become that kind of a person
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.03,0:50:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and that is what is valued.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.03,0:50:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The willingness then to become
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.03,0:50:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,a forgiving person
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.03,0:51:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,who nurtures all of life
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.06,0:51:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,non-judgmentally
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.06,0:51:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,automatically brings about within yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.06,0:51:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the very healing nature
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.06,0:51:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,a condition of good health.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.06,0:51:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The beginning to see
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.09,0:51:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the perfection of all things
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.09,0:51:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,how all things work out for the good.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.09,0:51:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How can illness be
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.09,0:51:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,held in that context?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.09,0:51:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,For the person who is oriented
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.60,0:51:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,such in the direction in which
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.60,0:51:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,we're talking today
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.60,0:51:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,then illness merely becomes
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.60,0:51:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,something that is coming up
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.64,0:51:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to be healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.64,0:51:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We look at the illness then
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.64,0:51:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,as bringing up a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.64,0:51:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The illness is saying
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.64,0:51:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,please heal what I stand for
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.64,0:51:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,what I symbolize.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.64,0:51:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please heal your guiltiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.92,0:51:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please heal your self-hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.92,0:51:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please heal your limiting thought forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.92,0:51:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please move up to loving me
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.92,0:51:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,so that I can be healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.92,0:51:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the illness
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.92,0:51:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is a demand
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.92,0:51:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to grow spiritually.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.92,0:51:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an incessant
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.92,0:52:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,gadfly
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.92,0:52:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that tells us
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.92,0:52:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that something is out
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.92,0:52:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,something needs to be looked at
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.92,0:52:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to be held in a different way.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.92,0:52:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You see because it is not
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.92,0:52:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the events of life
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.92,0:52:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but how we hold them
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.92,0:52:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that creates our reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.92,0:52:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Events in and of themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.92,0:52:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,have no power
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.92,0:52:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to affect how we feel
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.92,0:52:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,one way or another.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.92,0:52:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what our position is about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.92,0:52:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our judgment about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.92,0:52:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's how we decide to be with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.92,0:52:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.92,0:52:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our point of view.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.92,0:52:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the context.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.92,0:52:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we see
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.50,0:52:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,we are the creator then
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.50,0:52:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,of the meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.50,0:52:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the impact that it has on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.50,0:52:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stress comes from
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.50,0:52:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that very thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.50,0:52:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Giving it power over our lives
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.50,0:52:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,coming from the position of victim
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.50,0:52:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,putting the source of happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.50,0:52:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,outside of our life
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.50,0:52:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,denying the power of our own mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.50,0:53:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The healing then comes about
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.50,0:53:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,through the re-owning of the power
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.50,0:53:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the realization that we and we alone
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.50,0:53:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,create
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.50,0:53:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the meaning of any
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.50,0:53:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,circumstance, event,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.50,0:53:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,place, position or thing
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.50,0:53:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,any person in our life.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.50,0:53:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We are the one that creates the meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.88,0:53:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Our position, the way we hold it then
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.88,0:53:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that either becomes
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.88,0:53:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,a source of healing
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.88,0:53:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,or a source of illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.88,0:53:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We are the one that determines that.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.88,0:53:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's her little pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.88,0:53:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.88,0:53:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,we begin to see that the body
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.88,0:53:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is like a little marionette.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.88,0:53:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You know it sort of happily goes about its way
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.88,0:53:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,energy fuels of joyfulness and gladness.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.88,0:53:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You see it just sort of does
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.88,0:53:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,what it does automatically
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.88,0:53:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,without much thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.88,0:53:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Healthy means we pay less and less
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.88,0:53:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,attention to the body
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.88,0:53:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and that which we do
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.88,0:53:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,which the world would call health giving
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.88,0:53:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is out of appreciation
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.88,0:53:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,it's an expression of how we are
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.88,0:53:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,with that body.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.88,0:54:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You see we aren't giving away
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.88,0:54:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,our power as source.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.88,0:54:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Being healthy means you've re-owned
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.88,0:54:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,your power as source.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.88,0:54:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not giving away the source
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.88,0:54:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,of health of the body to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.27,0:54:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The exercising we do
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.27,0:54:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,is out of the joyfulness
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.27,0:54:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,in experiencing the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.27,0:54:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So we don't say that swimming
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.27,0:54:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,is what causes the body
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.27,0:54:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,to be healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.27,0:54:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We come from the position
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.27,0:54:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,that because we enjoy the body
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.27,0:54:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,we enjoy its activity
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.27,0:54:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,such as swimming.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.65,0:54:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So those activities which the world
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.65,0:54:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,consider healthy
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.65,0:54:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,then are coming out of the expression
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.65,0:54:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,of one's inner sense of aliveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.65,0:54:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The joy
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.65,0:54:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,in allowing the body's
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.65,0:54:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,expression in ways
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.65,0:54:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,that the world considers healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.65,0:54:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Not because they're causal
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.65,0:54:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,those are the effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.65,0:54:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The healthy enjoyment of the body then
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.65,0:54:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,is the effect of the mental attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.65,0:54:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at it as something pleasurable.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.65,0:55:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore we come to a
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.65,0:55:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,lovingness of the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.65,0:55:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not a narcissistic
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.65,0:55:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,self-glorification.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.65,0:55:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a muscle man
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.65,0:55:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,a picture in the photo magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.65,0:55:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Not out of desiringness
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.65,0:55:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,not out of pridefulness
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.65,0:55:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,not out of narcissism
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.65,0:55:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,but out of a lovingness
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.65,0:55:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and a gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.65,0:55:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We say ah little body
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.65,0:55:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you've served me well
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.65,0:55:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.65,0:55:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate you
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.65,0:55:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I value you
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.65,0:55:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,See we know we are not the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.81,0:55:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If you lose your right arm
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.81,0:55:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll still say I am me.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.81,0:55:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If you lose your left arm
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.81,0:55:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,if you lose both legs
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.81,0:55:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll still be saying I am me.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.81,0:55:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If we take off the ears
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.81,0:55:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,progressively the body diminishes
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.81,0:55:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,to practically nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.81,0:55:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and yet the sense of self
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.81,0:55:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,is ever with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.97,0:55:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the healthy person
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.97,0:55:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,begins to develop a sense of self
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.97,0:55:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,that is independent of external events
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.97,0:56:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and independent
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.97,0:56:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,of being the body itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.97,0:56:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The person is aware
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.97,0:56:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,that the body is the body
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.97,0:56:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,of events but I am me.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.97,0:56:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And that which I am
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.97,0:56:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,is really untouched by these events.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.97,0:56:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The self that wakes up every morning
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.97,0:56:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,before it even begins to remember
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.97,0:56:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,you know name and address
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.97,0:56:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and where you are
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.97,0:56:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and what you're supposed to do today
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.97,0:56:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,that self remains unimpaired.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.97,0:56:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The innocence of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.97,0:56:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,the hardware of the computer
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.97,0:56:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,is unaffected by the software
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.97,0:56:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,the events that go through life.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.97,0:56:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And so a healthy attitude
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.97,0:56:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,is one which does not put
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.97,0:56:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the person in transitory.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.00,0:56:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,When we look back at this chart
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.00,0:56:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.26,0:56:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happened here
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.26,0:56:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,is that the person has placed
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.26,0:56:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,their survival on something
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.26,0:56:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,outside of themself.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.26,0:56:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This something outside of oneself
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.26,0:56:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,is always transitory
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.26,0:56:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and changing in nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.26,0:56:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We can say the one thing we know
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.26,0:57:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,about the world for certain
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.26,0:57:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,is that all things change.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.26,0:57:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,All things change.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.26,0:57:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Consequently if we put the source
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.26,0:57:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,of our survival on that
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.26,0:57:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,which is outside of ourself
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.26,0:57:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,our job, our possessions
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.26,0:57:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,a particular relationship
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.26,0:57:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,then we're merely setting ourself up
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.26,0:57:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,for the loss
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.26,0:57:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,of our health
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.26,0:57:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,because what's going to come up
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.26,0:57:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,first of all is fear of loss
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.26,0:57:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,even though that's not conscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.26,0:57:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You know if the source of your happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.26,0:57:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,is your title and your position
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.26,0:57:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and your address and the kind of car
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.26,0:57:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that you have etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.26,0:57:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,or even the beauty of the physical body
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.26,0:57:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that you have
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.26,0:57:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,then you're vulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.26,0:57:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So that vulnerability
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.26,0:57:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,is in the unconscious
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.26,0:57:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and it stores up a great deal of fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.26,0:57:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore people's lives become
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.26,0:57:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,endlessly to reinforce
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.26,0:57:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and protect themselves from the loss
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.26,0:57:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,of those things upon which
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.90,0:57:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,they have put their survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.90,0:57:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The healthy person realizes
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.90,0:58:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the true nature of who they really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.90,0:58:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That they are something far beyond that.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.90,0:58:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That they are the one
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.90,0:58:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that gives those things value.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.90,0:58:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That they are temporary enjoyment
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.90,0:58:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,but their survival doesn't depend on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.90,0:58:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We said that when you move up
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.28,0:58:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,into this energy fuel
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.28,0:58:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,called acceptance
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.28,0:58:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,one has stopped giving one's power
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.28,0:58:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,away to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.28,0:58:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,One has begun to accept
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.28,0:58:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that I am the source of my happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.28,0:58:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That if you put a person like that
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.28,0:58:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,on a desert island and come back a year later
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.28,0:58:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,you know they'll have a coconut business going
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.28,0:58:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and they'll have found a new relationship
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.28,0:58:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and they'll build a tree house in the tree
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.28,0:58:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and they'll be teaching the children algebra.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.28,0:58:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That they have the capacity
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.28,0:58:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,to recreate for themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.28,0:58:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the source of happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.28,0:58:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,comes from the realization
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.28,0:58:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that I myself am the source of that happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.28,0:58:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I myself am the source of health.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.28,0:58:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't depend on epidemics.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.28,0:58:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't depend on what is out there in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.28,0:58:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't depend on what I eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.41,0:58:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,When we really realize that
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.41,0:59:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,then we begin to transcend
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.41,0:59:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and no longer be at the effect
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.41,0:59:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,of all these false belief systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.41,0:59:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And so what kind of a life
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.41,0:59:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,is possible then?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.41,0:59:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes from canceling these belief systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.41,0:59:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind says,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.41,0:59:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,uh-oh, you cancel these belief systems
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.48,0:59:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're really going to be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.48,0:59:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see here is a mind that has placed its security
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.48,0:59:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,it's based its security
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.48,0:59:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,on the worshipping of fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.51,0:59:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The worshipping of fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.51,0:59:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It is saying, by paying attention
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.51,0:59:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,to these fearful thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.51,0:59:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and complying with them
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.51,0:59:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,that's why
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.51,0:59:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I am alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.51,0:59:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A mind like that says
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.51,0:59:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the reason my house hasn't been robbed
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.51,0:59:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,is because I lock all my doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.51,0:59:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't see
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.83,0:59:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,that it's the power of the thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.83,0:59:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind thinks
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.83,0:59:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,if the doors are locked
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.83,0:59:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,the house won't be robbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.83,0:59:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the power of the mind
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.83,0:59:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,that's keeping the house from being robbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.37,0:59:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't the locking of the doors at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.37,0:59:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,As anybody knows
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.37,1:00:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,an accomplished thief will go through any lock.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.37,1:00:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no lock made that will hold back an accomplished thief.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.37,1:00:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll go through the window.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.37,1:00:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got your doors locked.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.44,1:00:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Zip, zip, zip, they're in through the window.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.44,1:00:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Zip, zip, zip, they're through the ceiling.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.44,1:00:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They're through the roof.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.44,1:00:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They're through the wall.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.44,1:00:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody wants in.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.44,1:00:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not kid ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.44,1:00:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They're going to get in.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.44,1:00:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Even an amateur like myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.44,1:00:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me 20 minutes
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.44,1:00:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and a trunk load of tools
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.44,1:00:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm going to be in that house.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.85,1:00:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the power of the thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.85,1:00:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The power of the belief.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.85,1:00:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't the lock.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.85,1:00:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the power of the belief.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.85,1:00:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The willingness to undo its mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.85,1:00:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The willingness to be
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.85,1:00:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,forgiving and compassionate.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.85,1:00:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The realization through wisdom
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.24,1:00:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,that I make myself victim
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.24,1:00:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,when I place the source of happiness
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.24,1:00:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,outside myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.24,1:00:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And so what happens is
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.24,1:00:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,we begin to recontextualize our life.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.24,1:01:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We begin to say
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.24,1:01:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,what is it that gives my life meaning?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.24,1:01:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it that I really value?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.24,1:01:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it that if you removed
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.24,1:01:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,from my life
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.24,1:01:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,if you took away my job
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.24,1:01:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and you took away my position
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.24,1:01:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,what meaning would my life have then?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.24,1:01:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What would it be worth?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.24,1:01:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I willing to die for?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.24,1:01:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And so some introspection
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.24,1:01:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and spiritual movement is necessary
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.24,1:01:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,to achieve a state of well-being.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.24,1:01:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The feeling that one's life
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.24,1:01:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,is significant.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.24,1:01:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That we make a difference in the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.81,1:01:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't need the attention
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.81,1:01:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,that illness brings to us
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.81,1:01:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,because our sense of importance
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.81,1:01:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,comes about through the realization
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.81,1:01:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and willingness of our real self.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.81,1:01:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And so general growth
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.81,1:01:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,in the whole field
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.81,1:01:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,of spiritual development
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.81,1:01:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,brings about a condition of health.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.81,1:01:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And it can do so quite rapidly.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.81,1:01:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,To change your position
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.81,1:01:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,to let go a certain limiting belief
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.81,1:01:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't take very long at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.81,1:01:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,First is the realization
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.81,1:02:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,that you have the power to do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.81,1:02:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And secondly
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.81,1:02:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,is the willingness to try it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.81,1:02:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,To verify through your own experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.81,1:02:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't necessary
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.81,1:02:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,to take the words of others.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.81,1:02:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The words of others are only an inspiration.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.81,1:02:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You have enough faith in them
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.81,1:02:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,to say, well, it sounds so
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.81,1:02:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm willing to give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.81,1:02:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore in my own particular
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.81,1:02:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,personal experience
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.91,1:02:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,as well as clinical experience
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.91,1:02:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen illnesses go in a matter of
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.91,1:02:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,minutes, days, weeks, months
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.91,1:02:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the most a chronic illness
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.91,1:02:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,that lasted for 25 years
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.91,1:02:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,perhaps took two years
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.20,1:02:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,but it was constantly doing the processes
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.20,1:02:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,that I've described today.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.20,1:02:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The willingness to accept the power of mind
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.20,1:02:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the willingness to never allow the mind
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.20,1:02:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,to say something negative
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.20,1:02:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,without challenging it
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.20,1:02:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and replacing it with a positive thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.20,1:02:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The willingness to let go
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.20,1:02:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,being judgmental towards ourselves and others
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.20,1:02:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,as a result of the letting go of the negative.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.20,1:02:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is this so?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.48,1:02:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so because
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.48,1:03:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy field of that which you are
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.48,1:03:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,which gives us
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.48,1:03:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,an intense sense of aliveness
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.48,1:03:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,when we let go of the obstacles to it
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.48,1:03:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,is ever present.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.48,1:03:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What we call bliss
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.48,1:03:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,is the vibration of life itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.48,1:03:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We could call all that is
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.48,1:03:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,at the top of this chart
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.48,1:03:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is God
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.48,1:03:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is spirit
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.48,1:03:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is one's higher power
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.48,1:03:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,what Krishnamurti calls what is
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.48,1:03:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,isness, beingness
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.48,1:03:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy of that is the energy of life itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.48,1:03:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Constantly present, ever present.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.48,1:03:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the sun
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.12,1:03:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,it is always shining
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.12,1:03:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,but because of these clouds here
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.12,1:03:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,we don't experience it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.12,1:03:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not necessary to program ourselves
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.12,1:03:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,with the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.12,1:03:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It is only necessary to remove
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.12,1:03:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is false.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.12,1:03:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The removal of the clouds from the sky
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.12,1:03:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the elimination of the negative
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.12,1:03:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,allows one to experience
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.12,1:03:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy fields
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.12,1:03:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,of that which is positive.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.12,1:04:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So it is only the removal of the negative
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.12,1:04:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,that is necessary.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.12,1:04:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The willingness to let go
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.12,1:04:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,of habits of negative thinking, etc.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.12,1:04:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The removal
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.54,1:04:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,of the obstacles
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.54,1:04:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,through the experiencing of this
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.54,1:04:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,will result in an increasing sense
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.54,1:04:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,of aliveness.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.54,1:04:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,With it, a joy of one's own existence.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.54,1:04:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,As this joy
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.54,1:04:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,of one's own existence comes in
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.54,1:04:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,first subtly and then stronger and stronger
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.54,1:04:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,there is a diminished
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.67,1:04:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,awareness even of the presence
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.67,1:04:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,of the body.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.67,1:04:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,One's physicalness
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.67,1:04:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,as one gets up into higher levels of happiness
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.67,1:04:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,there is a joyfulness
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.67,1:04:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the body is looked to as a source of pleasure
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.67,1:04:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,it is held as a pleasure
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.67,1:04:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,a pleasurable
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.73,1:04:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,enjoyable experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.73,1:04:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But as we move towards
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.73,1:04:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the top of the box
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.73,1:04:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the experiencing of the body
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.73,1:04:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,begins to diminish altogether.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.73,1:04:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a progressive experiencing
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.73,1:04:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,of joy which is diffuse.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.73,1:04:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There is an inner progressive
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.73,1:05:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,state of serenity accompanied by
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.73,1:05:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,a peaceful blissfulness.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.73,1:05:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And at this point
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.73,1:05:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the experience of the body
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.73,1:05:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,may disappear altogether
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.73,1:05:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,into sort of a sublime
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.73,1:05:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,state in which one is
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.73,1:05:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,joyful
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.73,1:05:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,aliveness.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.73,1:05:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,One is that which is
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.73,1:05:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,loving bliss.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.73,1:05:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,At that point the awareness of the body
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.73,1:05:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,may be almost nil.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.73,1:05:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as though it's present in the room
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.73,1:05:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's no more
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.73,1:05:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,important than anything else
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.73,1:05:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,in the room.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.76,1:05:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That loss of identification
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.76,1:05:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,with the body.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.76,1:05:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And we watch the body from that viewpoint
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.76,1:05:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,going about its business happily
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.76,1:05:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but we are no more concerned
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.76,1:05:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,about it than we are
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.76,1:05:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,anything else in the room.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.76,1:05:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That loss of identification
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.76,1:05:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,with the separate limited self.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.76,1:05:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The loss of identification
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.76,1:05:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,with the limited physical.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.76,1:05:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And with it of course the body
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.76,1:05:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,is expressing the absolute truth
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.76,1:06:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the infinite truth
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.76,1:06:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that one is the infinite beingness
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.76,1:06:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.76,1:06:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore the value
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.96,1:06:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,of replacing a negative thought
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.96,1:06:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,into the empty
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.96,1:06:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,space of that
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.96,1:06:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,in the place that we just cancel
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.96,1:06:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,we place the statement
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.96,1:06:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I am an infinite being and I am not
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.96,1:06:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,subject to that.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.96,1:06:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I am an infinite being and I am not subject to that.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.96,1:06:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So everything that we cancel
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.96,1:06:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,we replace with the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.96,1:06:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,In place of the negative thought
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.98,1:06:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,we put something in that's positive
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.98,1:06:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,because we choose to love
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.98,1:06:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,ourself instead.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.98,1:06:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So we can also use the form we can say
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.98,1:06:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I cancel that. I no longer buy that.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.98,1:06:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not subject to that.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.98,1:06:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead I choose to love myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.98,1:06:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead I choose to love myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.98,1:06:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we see that
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.98,1:06:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,lovingness then
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.98,1:06:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is the great healer.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.98,1:06:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We have within our capacity
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.98,1:06:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,within the power within us
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.98,1:06:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,all the powers of self healing.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.98,1:06:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,All we have to do is remove the obstacles.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.98,1:07:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect health
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.98,1:07:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is an expression then
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.98,1:07:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,of spiritual awareness.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.98,1:07:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The willingness to let go
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.98,1:07:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,of the negative
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.98,1:07:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and allowing it to be replaced by that
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.98,1:07:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,which is loving.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.04,1:07:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So the physical expression then
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.04,1:07:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,is of this energy field.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.04,1:07:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sickness is merely an expression
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.04,1:07:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,of this energy field
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.04,1:07:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,down here
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.04,1:07:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,given form by what is held in mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.04,1:07:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Physical health
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.17,1:07:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,is merely an expression
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.17,1:07:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,of a positive energy field
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.17,1:07:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,reinforced by our
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.17,1:07:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,willingness to commit
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.17,1:07:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,to compassion and forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.17,1:07:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That which I am
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.17,1:07:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,includes the body
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.17,1:07:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,not limited to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.24,1:07:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That which I am chooses to love it
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.24,1:07:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to value it
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.88,1:07:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to be appreciative of it
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.88,1:07:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to be grateful for it
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.94,1:07:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to enjoy the sense of aliveness.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.94,1:07:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We get into
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.94,1:07:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the joy of the experiencing
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.94,1:08:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,of experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.94,1:08:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We get more and more into the awareness
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.94,1:08:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,of the joy and the thankfulness
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.94,1:08:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,for our existence.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.94,1:08:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The existence of what?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.94,1:08:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The existence of our consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.94,1:08:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The body is then included
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.94,1:08:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,within the field of consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.94,1:08:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We come to the surprising thought
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.94,1:08:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that the body
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.94,1:08:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,is within the mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.94,1:08:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Most people
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.94,1:08:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,having a limited belief system
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.94,1:08:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,will think that the mind
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.94,1:08:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,is somewhere up here.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.94,1:08:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually when you experience experience
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.94,1:08:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,if you try to localize it
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.94,1:08:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,you will see that it is everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.94,1:08:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,When you experience a thought
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.94,1:08:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,it is being experienced everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.04,1:08:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The thought that it is occurring
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.04,1:08:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,somewhere in here
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.04,1:08:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,within your system
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.04,1:08:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,it is a thought about thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.68,1:08:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Inner experience will tell you
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.68,1:08:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that the experience of a thought
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.68,1:08:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the experience of the body
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.68,1:08:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,is occurring everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.68,1:08:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It is occurring in consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.68,1:08:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand that the body
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.68,1:09:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,is sitting in the chair
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.68,1:09:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but where is that understanding
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.68,1:09:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,being experienced?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.68,1:09:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That understanding is being experienced
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.68,1:09:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,in no specific place.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.68,1:09:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It is happening within
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.68,1:09:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,your consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.87,1:09:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The health then is really
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.87,1:09:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,addressing ourselves
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.87,1:09:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,to the nature of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.87,1:09:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The body then is coming out
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.87,1:09:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,of our sense of aliveness
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.87,1:09:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,which is coming out of our
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.87,1:09:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,sense of appreciation
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.87,1:09:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,for our own existence.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.87,1:09:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,In this talk we have repeated
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.87,1:09:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,certain things over and over
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.87,1:09:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the mind's resistance
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.93,1:09:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,to accepting the truth of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.93,1:09:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Right brain learning is really
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.93,1:09:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,one of becoming familiar
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.93,1:09:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,constantly re-exposing ourselves
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.93,1:09:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,until it becomes natural.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.93,1:09:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it difficult when it comes
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.93,1:09:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,to healing and health?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.93,1:09:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It is because we are really reversing
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.93,1:09:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,the mind's belief in causality.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.93,1:09:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We are saying that the physical
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.93,1:09:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,is the expression of the mental
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.25,1:10:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and not vice versa.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.25,1:10:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You see the world would like to say
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.25,1:10:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and that it is the other way around
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.25,1:10:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that cause is within the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.25,1:10:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Cause is within the powers
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.25,1:10:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,within the virus.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.25,1:10:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The power is within the bacteria.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.25,1:10:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Even medications work because
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.25,1:10:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,it is the belief in the power
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.25,1:10:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,of the medication.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.25,1:10:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We certainly see this with scientific research
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.25,1:10:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,into the nature of placebos.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.25,1:10:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Placebos alone will cure 35%
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.25,1:10:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,generally of people with any given ailment.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.25,1:10:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the suggestion
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.25,1:10:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that this pill will heal it
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.25,1:10:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,35% of the time
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.25,1:10:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,is all that is sufficient.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.25,1:10:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Realizing then
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.99,1:10:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,that we are making a major move
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.99,1:10:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,in consciousness allows us
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.99,1:10:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,to value
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.99,1:10:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,all of our knowledge about
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.99,1:10:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness and health
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.99,1:10:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,to use it as a springboard
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.99,1:10:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,to our own spiritual growth and development.
